]. 
<collectorName id="26BDC7F2FFA0B83FFCED4EEC666AF85B" box="[845,862,1953,1976]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">It</collectorName>
is impossible to establish the identity of the latter specimens until more material of 
<taxonomicName id="4C48D9A7FFA0B83FFDAE4E886788F83F" authorityName="Kaydan &amp; Gullan" authorityYear="2012" box="[526,700,1988,2012]" class="Insecta" family="Pseudococcidae" genus="Ferrisia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ecuadorensis">
